description
From: http://myeigenharp.wordpress.com/2013/3/27/octave-talker/
Octave talker, first solution altered to use a global variable:
  variable octave step

script
empty join
octave talker listen
1 called 1 cancel
" main keygroup hey octave by variable octave step down " when 1 called 1 do
2 called 1 cancel
" main keygroup hey octave by variable octave step up " when 2 called 1 do
